        {
            "id": "",
            "content_html": "<h2>707. 设计链表</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/problems/design-linked-list/description/\">题目链接</a><br>\n题意：在链表中实现以下功能</p>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"https://remsait.com/posts/设计链表\" target=\"_blank\">https://remsait.com/posts/设计链表</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
            "url": "https://remsait.com/posts/设计链表",
            "title": "设计链表",
            "date_modified": "2025-08-06T11:39:18.000Z",
            "date_published": "2025-08-14T02:14:17.571Z",
            "author": {
                "name": "西柿",
                "url": "https://valaxy.site"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "",
            "content_html": "<h4>迭代</h4>\n<p>1.迭代法称为辗转法，不断的用变量旧值求出新值，即对一组指令循环执行，最终得到新值作为结果。<br>\n2.在代码中表现为在一个循环内，不断循环最终得到结果。</p>\n<h4>递归</h4>\n<p>1.定义：递归</p>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"https://remsait.com/posts/迭代-递归-分治\" target=\"_blank\">https://remsait.com/posts/迭代-递归-分治</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
            "url": "https://remsait.com/posts/迭代-递归-分治",
            "title": "迭代&递归&分治",
            "date_modified": "2023-04-02T20:02:43.000Z",
            "date_published": "2025-08-14T02:14:17.571Z",
            "author": {
                "name": "西柿",
                "url": "https://valaxy.site"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "",
            "content_html": "<p>难度：中等<br>\n题目链接：<a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/problems/reorder-list/\">https://leetcode.cn/problems/reorder-list/</a><br>\n![](<a href=\"https://cloudflare.remsait.com/img/2023\">https://cloudflare.remsait.com/img/2023</a></p>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"https://remsait.com/posts/重排链表\" target=\"_blank\">https://remsait.com/posts/重排链表</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
            "url": "https://remsait.com/posts/重排链表",
            "title": "重排链表",
            "date_modified": "2023-04-03T18:14:24.000Z",
            "date_published": "2025-08-14T02:14:17.571Z",
            "author": {
                "name": "西柿",
                "url": "https://valaxy.site"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "",
            "content_html": "<p>链表是一种通过指针串联在一起的线性结构，每一个节点由两部分组成，一个是数据域一个是指针域（存放指向下一个节点的指针），最后一个节点的指针域指向 null<br>\n链表的入口节点称为链表的头结点，也就是</p>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"https://remsait.com/posts/链表\" target=\"_blank\">https://remsait.com/posts/链表</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
            "url": "https://remsait.com/posts/链表",
            "title": "链表",
            "date_modified": "2023-04-03T18:04:57.000Z",
            "date_published": "2025-08-14T02:14:17.571Z",
            "author": {
                "name": "西柿",
                "url": "https://valaxy.site"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "",
            "content_html": "<p>难度：中等<br>\n链接：<a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/problems/sort-list/\">Sort List</a><br>\n题意：在时间复杂度为O(nlogn)内，空间复杂度为O(1)内对给定首元结</p>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"https://remsait.com/posts/链表排序\" target=\"_blank\">https://remsait.com/posts/链表排序</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
