        {
            "id": "",
            "content_html": "<h2>19. 删除链表的倒数第 N 个结点</h2>\n<p>[题目链接](<a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/problems/remove-nth-node-from-end-of-list/descripti\">https://leetcode.cn/problems/remove-nth-node-from-end-of-list/descripti</a></p>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"https://remsait.com/posts/删除链表的倒数第N个节点\" target=\"_blank\">https://remsait.com/posts/删除链表的倒数第N个节点</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
