        {
            "id": "",
            "content_html": "<h2>Logistic回归概念</h2>\n<h3>概述</h3>\n<p>  Logistic回归又叫逻辑回归，实际上是用来做分类，主要思想是根据现有数据对分类边界线建立回归公式，以此进行分类</p>\n<h3>Sigmoi</h3>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"https://remsait.com/posts/Logistic回归\" target=\"_blank\">https://remsait.com/posts/Logistic回归</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
            "url": "https://remsait.com/posts/Logistic回归",
            "title": "Logistic回归",
            "date_modified": "2024-09-06T10:52:42.000Z",
            "date_published": "2025-08-14T02:14:17.568Z",
            "author": {
                "name": "西柿",
                "url": "https://valaxy.site"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "",
            "content_html": "<h2>支持向量机 概述</h2>\n<p>支持向量机（SVM）是一种监督学习算法</p>\n<ul>\n<li>支持向量 就是离分隔超平面最近的那些点。</li>\n<li>机 就是表示一种算法，而不是表示机器</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>支持向量机 场景</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>要给左右两边的点</li>\n</ul>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"https://remsait.com/posts/SVM\" target=\"_blank\">https://remsait.com/posts/SVM</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
            "url": "https://remsait.com/posts/SVM",
            "title": "支持向量机",
            "date_modified": "2024-09-12T09:35:20.000Z",
            "date_published": "2025-08-14T02:14:17.568Z",
            "author": {
                "name": "西柿",
                "url": "https://valaxy.site"
            }
        },
        {
